PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of MANITOBA which will permit the Department of Natural Resources to make improvements to an access road situated on the grounds of THE PAS AIRPORT, known as the Orok siding road, and to use and maintain the road for a term of forty (40) years, and thus provide them with easier access to their sewage lagoon.
